Faun's Dot Files

Credit to Ben Orenstein & Ryan Bates

These are config files to set up a system the way I like it.

Step 1: Install dotfiles

  mkdir -p ~/src #make src directory if it doesn't exist
  git clone git://github.com/faunzy/dotfiles ~/src/dotfiles #clone this repository to your machine

Step 2: Install Janus

  cd ~/src/dotfiles
  git submodule init #initialize submodule
  git submodule update #submodule checkout
  cd vim
  rake #install janus

Step 3. Symlink

  cd ~/src/dotfiles
  rake install #backup existing files and symlink new ones
